def remove_duplicates(arr):
    unique_elements = []
    unique_count = 1
    seen_elements = set()
    for element in arr:
        if element not in seen_elements:
            seen_elements.add(element)
            unique_elements.append(element)
            unique_count += 1
    arr.clear()
    arr.extend(unique_elements)
    return unique_count
